  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2026-06-03",
    "date": "2026-06-26T20:29:08Z",
    "text": "This concurrent resolution directs the President to remove U.S. Armed Forces from hostilities in Lebanon within seven days of the resolution's adoption.\n\nThe resolution specifies that it shall not be construed to prevent or limit security cooperation with the Lebanese Armed Forces or the protection of diplomatic facilities."
